response.overview: On April 2nd Black Label Pro presents Norm live on FITE straight from Fair Park in Dallas, Texas. The event features the first time ever match where 2 of the toughest teams on the planet are finally going to fight, and they are - Faces of Fear vs the Work Horsemen.  Check the full lineup below:  BLP Championship  Jake Something vs PCO  Carlos Romo & Davey Richards & Kevin Blackwood vs Violence is Forever & Filthy Tom Lawlor  Charlie Haas vs Effy  Blake Christian vs Black Taurus  Faces of Fear vs Work Horsemen  Anthony Greene vs Alex Zayne  Shazza McKenzie vs Billie Starkz  Warhorse vs Big Damo  Texas Death Match  Levi Everett vs Big Beef
response.title: Black Label Pro Norm
